Posts.Content: Hello, I have very special news to share with you day. My name is Nancy and I am currently involved in a non profit organization to help people who are suffering with cancer, depression, weight loss, or any other health related issues. There is no cost associated for my help but their is a limit to how many people I can help at one time. I will be working with you one on one with your health matters online. My personal email address is: [emailÂ protected] My backgound information Dr. Nancy Frezoni obtained a BS in biology from the University of Washington in 1986. She earned an ND from Bastyr University in 1997, and then completed two years of residency at Bastyr Center for Natural Health. Currently a clinical faculty member at the center, Dr. Fresonke practices family medicine with a special interest in physical medicine, sports medicine, pediatrics and women?s health.
